result.name: Moriya

reviews.text: Very tasty grilled beef set I had. I think the price is very reasonable and good service. Definitely coming back again.
Price reasonable, quality food, but only one waiter, who is always busy.  (Maybe he is the owner of the restaurant.)

Charging a 10% service charge for a bowl of pretty ordinary take away noodles (total price $110 HK) is a nothing but a rip off. 

I used to like the food and the people. The place is looking seriously tired. 

However this evening, after question my 10% service charge on take-away food, the chef arrogantly pointed to his disposable plastic pates as items I were somehow expected to pay an additional $10 HK for. In what ended up being a pretty ordinary bowl of noodles with zero meat. 

I did not take up a table, seat nor ask for water... if fact I waited outside. I was confused later as to why they even had customers.

The meal resembled something like a regular meal at Changi POW camp in 1944. Nothing substantial. Certainly not for $110.

It was insulting.

This was the first time following a 2 year absence I had returned to this place. I wish I could have said “improved”. But attitude, price and the food quality is not just worse than before - it was appalling. 

I won’t be going back. Food is nasty and the attitude is worse. Far better places to eat for half the price within 50 metres. 

Summary: used to be good. Spend you money on something which will give you double the enjoyment - at half the price.
Good food and good place to have dinner
Awesome food and super friendly and helpful staffs!!

reviews.text: 食物質素唔錯，但餐廳內油煙太多，應改善廚房通風
Very tasty grilled beef set I had. I think the price is very reasonable and good service. Definitely coming back again.
Price reasonable, quality food, but only one waiter, who is always busy.  (Maybe he is the owner of the restaurant.)

與同事在此餐廳午餐，體驗極差。
點了食物之後，兩位同事的餐點到後，我自己點的食物卻苦等半小時以上都沒有任何回應，店員亦沒有協助追餐。
良久之後終於有食物送到，奈何所點的照燒雞飯幾乎變成炭燒雞飯，雞的面積約有1/4是焦掉的。同事的網燒牛則比較正常，奈何部份較薄的位置也是焦掉，甚至有苦味。飯亦是用口感極差的米飯，口感糜爛。
許久沒有食過這麼差的食店。價錢昂貴， 品質差勁， 服務九流。
每次來都好好味
